data.description: Welcome to this highly desirable corner lot brick single-family home featuring 5 bedrooms plus a den and 2 full bathrooms. This charming property boasts numerous appealing features, including a new roof installed in 2022, a recently replaced water heater in 2023, and elegant hardwood floors throughout.  The kitchen has been tastefully remodeled with granite countertops, modern cabinetry, and stainless steel appliances, all installed in 2022. Experience ample natural light through windows replaced in 2021. The property also offers a recently updated patio and accommodates more than six cars in the parking area.  Enjoy a spacious front and backyard, perfect for your entertainment needs. This home is ideally located in close proximity to public transportation, commuter routes, the library, schools, shopping centers, dining options, entertainment venues, and more.  This property is easy to show, and should you have any questions, feel free to reach out to helpful and cheerful listing agent. Don't miss the opportunity to visit this home!
